{"id": 533, "genre": 1001, "title": "等人等得要发疯的时候你都能干些啥？", "description": "作为一个过分靠谱的人，等待就是我必须承受的命运。", "record_count": 4944, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183601ipSIx95wXLfAeNWk.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-09-25T10:50:55Z", "options": [{"id": 13312, "content": "直接不等了，等他打电话过来找我！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 204974}, {"id": 15360, "content": "刷微博", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234096}, {"id": 14594, "content": "观察路人，企图从细节中得到一些不得了的事情…但大多数都是自作多情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 213014}, {"id": 14340, "content": "刷手机默默.", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 219507}, {"id": 16644, "content": "回家 等毛线 都要疯了的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 214264}, {"id": 13062, "content": "等男票他晚了会不自觉生气，然后怀疑人生", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 201224}, {"id": 14854, "content": "蹲马路牙子上装流浪者", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227127}, {"id": 13831, "content": "不会有我等别人的时候，都是别人等我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 212177}, {"id": 16137, "content": "买杯饮料刷小说，或者看看路人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 233291}, {"id": 13323, "content": "心急", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205164}, {"id": 17420, "content": "来回走，微博刷完刷朋友圈再看看时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252597}, {"id": 15885, "content": "给自己灌脑海鸡汤，外带自动修订功能", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 222933}, {"id": 13838, "content": "看电子书", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 212208}, {"id": 13586, "content": "看风景，心里数数", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 195692}, {"id": 16658, "content": "大吃一顿", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248348}, {"id": 13075, "content": "等个屁，走人", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 201451}, {"id": 15123, "content": "看看周围的漂亮妹妹", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 231622}, {"id": 13588, "content": "扮帅", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 209228}, {"id": 13077, "content": "看看手机聊聊天，刷刷新闻微博，找一个地方坐坐喝喝茶。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 198025}, {"id": 13078, "content": "听歌发呆", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 200866}, {"id": 13590, "content": "看马路.........发呆.......", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 209267}, {"id": 16662, "content": "欣赏路过的美女，顺便看到好看的要个号", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 176055}, {"id": 13591, "content": "发牢骚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 209211}, {"id": 13080, "content": "打开微信附近人，可以约的就先约出来打一炮在继续等待", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 197601}, {"id": 13336, "content": "找个店坐着点喝的接着塞耳机看手机。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205288}, {"id": 14616, "content": "观察路人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 223713}, {"id": 13081, "content": "不时低下头看手表，拉拉衣服，装装B", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 200603}, {"id": 13849, "content": "等人是我的工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 212372}, {"id": 13082, "content": "继续等", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 201618}, {"id": 13851, "content": "在要俄罗斯方块～～～真的很好玩，来人了有时候都停不下来～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 212414}, {"id": 13084, "content": "在人多的地方等人会不停的刷着手机，掩饰自己的尴尬。\n人少的地方等人会不停的刷着手机。\n自家楼下等人还是不停的刷着手机\n总的来说就是刷刷手机等人！！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 201730}, {"id": 15388, "content": "心里把要等的人骂个够，", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234249}, {"id": 13088, "content": "看美女", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 201879}, {"id": 13603, "content": "幻想他可能是被车撞了，或者遇见抢劫了什么的，我最善良了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 71739}, {"id": 13860, "content": "看好奇心日报??", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 210254}, {"id": 14884, "content": "脑子中恶补各种见到他那一刻，自己会如何骂他的情景！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 225062}, {"id": 16932, "content": "担心对方忘记了，担心自己来错地儿。。。百般核对以后觉得对方应该是死在路上了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250495}, {"id": 13093, "content": "不停的画圈圈……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 200310}, {"id": 13351, "content": "其实等人越久，他来的那一下更有满足感！我就一直想事情和等待，享受静心等待的感觉！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205634}, {"id": 14887, "content": "把奇迹暖暖两三个号的体力弄完", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227969}, {"id": 13096, "content": "观察周围的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 202162}, {"id": 13097, "content": "逛逛超市，逛逛街，再买杯饮料吃个甜品，最后叫对方等我。无比充实", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 202175}, {"id": 14634, "content": "催那个人…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 224413}, {"id": 14890, "content": "果断打开小说软件然后买点东西在店里坐好", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227401}, {"id": 16682, "content": "如果地上有格子或者图案，就变着法子的踩来踩去…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 246091}, {"id": 13099, "content": "看天，看人，看镜子～", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 202228}, {"id": 20267, "content": "走人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 269601}, {"id": 12844, "content": "哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 165451}, {"id": 14124, "content": "看街景，关注街边的路人，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215916}, {"id": 12845, "content": "打电话", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 134430}]}